name: Untitled Collision Game
description:
*No win or lose states yet so it's all scouts honor*

  • Collect all the Purple Boxes
  • Put them on the White Square
  • Watch out for people stealing the objects
  • Hit them with objects to stop them
  • and DO IT ALL in the time limit!

Please leave a comment with your Feedback below, we would love to hear it!

Game by Aaryan and Dana
